      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "卫小申",
        "卫院子"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卫小申上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "适才离了六龙潭，不要拔剑斩蛟龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，卫小申。在宋王驾前为臣。因俺面目丑陋，贬在家下，永不敍用。哪知我\n再没这样逍遥自在。前日忽然我姑妈有书到来，命我去往沙河救援。高弟约会\n我中途青莲洞相会。\n来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卫院子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "行囊可曾齐备了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "齐备多时。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "即刻起程，伺候了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卫小申、卫院子同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "卫小申→卫院子",
          "turns": 2
        },
        {
          "edge": "卫院子→卫小申",
          "turns": 2
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "念": 1,
          "白": 4
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "杨仙童"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨仙童上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "辞别了师父下山林，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，杨仙童。奉师父之命，搭救母亲回朝。天色尚早，驾云前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母子今日团圆庆，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨仙童下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "唱": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 1.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "卫小申",
        "杨仙童",
        "高能"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（高能上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "行过一程又一程，\n心忙似箭奔宋营。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卫小申内叫。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又听有人叫一声。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卫小申上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "几年不曾与贼战，\n盔不明来甲不鲜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "表兄来了。你难道不知救兵如救火，如何误得时刻？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看涧下有水，你我吃些再走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你去吃些，我在此等你。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卫小申下。杨仙童上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大路之上有黑风，\n按落云头看分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "面前有黑风，俺不免驾起五色祥云穿风而过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "风内必是妖和怪，\n先斩一剑命归阴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "高叫道童休动手，\n饶你不死留下名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这道童，好生无礼，穿风就过，使剑就砍，是何理也？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "中途路上使起黑风，想必是妖魔鬼怪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。你就通上名来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要问俺名姓，你且听了：我母玉芙蓉，当日征西路过花马天齐庙，产生下我，\n落地而亡，多蒙毗卢大仙救去，取名仙童，传俺兵法武艺，一十一载。今母\n亲围困沙河，师父命我下山搭救。你是何人阻路？"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是表弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺乃高能，与你乃姑表之亲。为因姑母有书到来，命我齐集表兄表弟前往搭救。\n不想此地相会，真乃天幸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是表兄，如此按落云头相敍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有理。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（过场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童、高能",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（表兄有礼）（表弟免礼）。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨仙童、高能同见礼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还有何人同行？"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还有你亲表兄卫小申。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他往哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "涧下饮水去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我且等他些。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卫小申上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里来的这么一个黑杂宗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓吓吓，骂不得。这就是你表兄，如何骂得？\n你不知道，只因当年姑母征西路过花马天齐庙，产生一子，落地而亡。蒙毗卢\n大仙救下，取名仙童，传授兵法武艺，前往沙河母子相会。这才是你嫡嫡亲亲\n表兄到了。上前见过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那作什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "表兄为什么打我？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你为什么骂我？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谁的见证？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "高大哥的见证。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我问来。\n高大哥，卫表兄说我骂了他，你可听见？"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你骂他，我不曾听见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "站着！你方才骂我小王八旦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "高大哥的见证。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥，我骂他没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用说了。正事要紧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我会奇门遁法，六甲灵文，呼风唤雨，撒豆成兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我会使黑风。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我会变猫变狗。撒谎不是东西，咱们大家试演试演。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天灵灵，地灵灵，我奉毗卢大仙法，豆兵速降。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鬼兵上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "勒退。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鬼兵下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黑风速降。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（八风旗同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "勒速退。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（八风旗同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "该你变了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "变！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卫小申下，猫形上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一大猫，待我着一死老鼠与你吃。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（猫形下，卫小申上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "变。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卫小申下，狗形上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一只大犬，待我撒泡尿与它。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（狗形下，卫小申上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谁先走？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "让你先走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三人作事好商量，\n要作元帅定主张。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卫小申下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先到就要印在掌，\n各使妙法逞豪强。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（高能下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见表兄都前行，\n驾起祥云奔番营。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨仙童下。卫小申上，高能随上，推倒高能，高能下，卫小申随下。杨仙童上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我母那里必挂望，\n赶至大营见萱堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨仙童下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "高能→卫小申",
