    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "七宝山中仙人救",
        "产生婴孩儿落地死",
        "兵卒",
        "卫小申",
        "师父命我把山下",
        "杨仙童",
        "玉芙蓉",
        "那年母亲征西去",
        "那贼全仗邪道术",
        "高能"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（兵卒引玉芙蓉同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二国不合动刀兵，\n领了圣命来战争。\n擒我上将十馀名。\n不知何日来救兵？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨仙童上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "按落云头来看真，\n旌旗展展是大营。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有人么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "兵卒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相烦通禀：说仙山杨道童求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "兵卒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少待。\n启元帅：营门外有仙山道童求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "引进来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "兵卒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。\n道童呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在这里。"
        },
        {
          "character": "兵卒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "着你进去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨仙童应，进。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅在上，道童即见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何处仙童，到此何干？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅容禀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "中军帐内一声禀，\n尊声萱堂听原因：\n天齐庙前把我生。\n兵法武艺教的精。\n特地前来救母亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "那年母亲征西去、七宝山中仙人救、师父命我把山下、玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听一言来吃一惊，\n当日征西有此情。\n既死怎能又重生？"
        },
        {
          "character": "产生婴孩儿落地死、杨仙童",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "毗卢大仙将儿救，\n师父取名杨仙童。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "用手扶起姣生子，\n只怕相逢在梦中。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲不必多疑，母子重逢不是作梦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，我儿坐了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀母亲：儿在中途遇见两个表兄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可是卫小申同高能么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他二人怎么不见？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还在后面。母亲，我们三人在中途打了东道，谁要先入大营就为元帅，后到者\n就为先行，第三到者还要认罚问罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这等说，元帅是我儿的了。你到营门外等候二位表兄便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿领命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨仙童出帐。高能上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "行过高山峻岭，\n且自收了黑风云。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你先到了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我早来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，元帅是你的了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那卫小申呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还在后面。你我在此等他一等。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卫小申上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他二人上了我的当，"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如何先到在营门？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你才来吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依你说是见过姑母的了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你此番进去，不用见礼了。\n二位表兄到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命他二人进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨仙童应。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命二位表兄进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申、高能",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侄儿参见姑母。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一路辛苦，只行常礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卫小申来到此间，见了我为何礼节全无？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个呢……"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将可曾齐见卫爷进帐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "兵卒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没有。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（高能向卫小申。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "过来，跪下。要打罚你呢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卫小申，命你攻打头阵，不得有误。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卫小申下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "高能、杨仙童听令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童、高能",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你二人带领三千人马，帮助卫小申成功。听我一令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与你二人一只令，\n后队接应卫小申。\n各自阵前要小心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "那贼全仗邪道术、杨仙童、高能",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高能",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "辞别元帅出大营，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "五营四哨去调兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨仙童、高能同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉芙蓉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今朝母子重相逢，\n喜得儿郎降来临。\n专等探子报军情。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（玉芙蓉下。）"
        }
